decks.notes: The deck focuses on utilizing artifacts and synergy between cards to generate explosive plays and overwhelm the opponent quickly. By combining powerful artifact creatures with cheap spells and mana acceleration, the deck aims to establish a strong board presence early on and maintain pressure throughout the game. The inclusion of Jeskai Ascendancy and other support cards further enhances the deck's ability to draw cards, control the board, and generate additional value. Overall, the deck aims to win fast through aggressive plays and efficient use of resources.
